about.summary: Create 'roxygen2' skeleton populated with information scraped from the within the function script. Also creates field entries for imports in the 'DESCRIPTION' and import in the 'NAMESPACE' files. Can be run from the R console or through the 'RStudio' 'addin' menu.

Create 'roxygen2' skeleton populated with information scraped from the within the function script. Also creates field entries for imports in the 'DESCRIPTION' and import in the 'NAMESPACE' files. Can be run from the R console or through the 'RStudio' 'addin' menu.

name: r-sinew
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '0.3.8' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-sinew
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/sinew_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/sinew/sinew_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 81b993655dfe2283513fff793d442d5bfe7c5e7ab514666d325bdb571f3ffdbd

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-cli
    - r-crayon
    - r-miniui
    - r-rematch2
    - r-rstudioapi
    - r-shiny
    - r-sos
    - r-stringi
    - r-yaml
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-cli
    - r-crayon
    - r-miniui
    - r-rematch2
    - r-rstudioapi
    - r-shiny
    - r-sos
    - r-stringi
    - r-yaml

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('sinew')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('sinew')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/metrumresearchgroup/sinew
  license: GPL-2.0-only OR GPL-3.0-only
  summary: Create 'roxygen2' skeleton populated with information scraped from the within the
    function script. Also creates field entries for imports in the 'DESCRIPTION' and
    import in the 'NAMESPACE' files. Can be run from the R console or through the 'RStudio'
    'addin' menu.
  license_family: GPL
  license_file:
    - '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'
    - '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-3'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - brendanf
